{"tid":261479,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺資訊科技比老一輩妖魔化","createTime":"2017-05-28T13:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T10:52:15.000Z","uid":118314,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d046aef829dffb56b9a68302ce8f02afae5964d3","tid":261479,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"同長輩飲茶有感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺唔覺近年好盛行一種「食飯唔好睇手機，會影響感情」嘅睇法<br />\n我心諗，你唔係覺得我唔用手機就會同你地有計傾啊嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一用手機/電腦，就話你唔健康，將你身上所有唔健康嘅特質賴晒落手機/電腦上面<br />\n你瘦係因為對太多電腦，你肥都係因為對太多電腦;<br />\n好眼訓係因為對太多電腦，訓唔著都係因為對太多電腦;<br />\n總之傷風感冒心血少全部都係因為用太多手機電腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日到黑剩係識係度講咩藍光，但佢地真係知咩係藍光咩? 個原理係乜? 晒9氣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好老實講，而家上網可以學到無窮盡嘅知識、可以得到國際即時新聞、可以知道呢排興D咩有乜好玩，班長輩唔識用就算，可唔可以唔好阻止社會向前進 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cda17014031d299d588a2b16afff465cf44e33","tid":261479,"uid":14799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"Any solution?"},{"pid":"498810e5130f080f18c62df20a1ea79180bf7527","tid":261479,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你瘦係因為對太多電腦，你肥都係因為對太多電腦;<br />\n好眼訓係因為對太多電腦，訓唔著都係因為對太多電腦;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e0f06892706ebacd2a71bcfebcccd9aca0c520","tid":261479,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Any solution?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同